'''''Canticle''''' by [[R.A. Salvatore]] is a ''[[Forgotten Realms]]'' novel first published in 1991. It is the first book of the [[The Cleric Quintet]] and introduces the characters [[Cadderly Bonaduce]], [[Danica Maupoissant]], and [[Ivan Bouldershoulder|Ivan]] and [[Pikel Bouldershoulder]].

{{quote|
High in the [[Snowflake Mountains]] sits the [[Edificant Library]], a place of scholarly study for [[priest]]s, [[bards]], and others. Now from the hidden vaults beneath the library a devastating [[Chaos Curse|curse]] is unleashed, and a young cleric must battle the terrifying creatures set loose by a malevolent, consuming essence.|Back-cover text from 2000 edition}}
